entries.femaleVariant: Did you get everything inside?
How is going, Foz? This gig treating you well?
Do you know how much our boss takes in from this trash?
I hate this place…
All right, enough slacking around. Get that shit off the street.
I've been chopping chrome for five years and I'm telling you – we don't do breaks.
I sit here all day, doing fuck all... I see your ugly face more than my input's input, you know what I mean?
What did you last see on TV?
I tell you, this new one is the next level.
He's the boss, isn't he? So he should live like one.
Hey, what if we stopped losing and started winning for once?
What's so good about it? I mean, the stuff she records.
Imagine that you smack her in the mouth. Yeah?
No, I hate that everyone here is dumber than bricks.
Who put sand in your ass?
We don't have enough methionine for today's batch.
This RTL… it won't make anyone foam a the mouth, will it? Because if it does we'll be out of biz.
I don't understand why they take it…
Did you see the crowd we got yesterday?
What the hell are you talking about? We charge five hundred to get in.
So? It's still worth it.
The hell? You see that?
Now the AC's busted?
Fuuuuuuuck... shitter's turned into a goddamn fountain.
Almost.
What you do mean "almost"? Grab a crate and get your ass moving.
It's my break. Chill.
If you're in such a hurry, you do it!
Looks like no one's taught you your place yet…
Well, I've been here four days, doing nothing but moving crates. And I fucking quit!
Relax. We'll add RTL and the weight will be right.
RTL?
Erythritol. It's like candy for grown-ups.
Do you have any clue what we're baking here?
Propylmethionine makes you trip so hard even an Animal would shit himself.
Do you really think a little synth sugar is going to hurt?
Nobody buys it because they like it. Except for the schizos.
So who buys it?
The fucking corps, who else?!
Maybe ten in all? The same as always.
Exactly. Did it ever occur to you that's a loss?
You know what five hundred times ten is? That's how much we pull in per night.
And how many nights do we do each month? Two? Maybe three?
Not if you count the cost of the implants.
You know how much that junk costs? Eight thousand.
Shiiiiiiit…
Meh.
Meh? What the fuck does "meh" mean? Huh?
You know, you could say something interesting once in a while.
A joke, whatever, I don't care.
We have nothing but time to kill in this dump.
Did you pick up any woman? Get laid?
Let's try food. Did you eat anything good lately?
Will you say anything?
Ugh…
How much?
Ten times what we make slumming here for a whole MONTH.
How do you know?
I've seen his pad. I know.
He's the boss because he can get any pussy to work for dirt.
It used to be that pussies were just pussies... Now we're the ones with our dicks in our hands.
Pussies like you.
Go on.
You and me load the crates into my old beater and take the high road.
That piece of junk? We wouldn't get past the first intersection before they dragged us out and splattered our brains on the pavement.
Any other genius ideas?
You've seen this already?
She records the craziest shit you can imagine and cranks the real-feel up real high.
Are you joking? I'm too young to go insane.
Christ, choom. Do  you know what a house of mirrors is?
Maybe.
It's like that, that's what she has in her HEAD.
For example?
OK.
Now when you play back the virtu, there you are, doing your thing, right?
Yeah. Obviously.
OK. Except then you see another guy smacking her up. Only it's somewhere else, and different.
And then another, and another.
OK, that is crazy. How does she do it?
I have no idea. If they're memories, I've never seen anything cleaner in my life.
House of mirrors, I tell you.
What's there to hate? That nobody checks on us and every day is chill?
That we don't have to stand outside all day in the rain?
Hey, the door is open. Walk out, no one will stop you.
That sucks so much, man, yeah.
Or I could just crack your skull, shut you up.
No one. I just hate it. It always smells like piss on a rotting corpse.
Take a walk to the docks. Your brain needs air.
I hate the docks, too. The whole city is one giant rot pile.
Something's not right…
And who the fuck's gonna clean that?
